1
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:17,310
[Sin and Love]

2
00:00:17,430 --> 00:00:21,310
[Episode 2]

3
00:00:30,060 --> 00:00:30,940
Police!

4
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:32,080
Is anyone in there?

5
00:00:35,820 --> 00:00:37,620
Sung Ho, you're still here.

6
00:00:38,340 --> 00:00:40,520
Officer Kwon was looking for you.

7
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,420
I covered for you.

8
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:48,520
Got it.

9
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:49,910
I'm leaving first.

10
00:01:00,370 --> 00:01:01,250
As expected,

11
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,250
you're a bad guy,

12
00:01:04,050 --> 00:01:04,780
Sung Ho.

13
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:21,780
You

14
00:01:23,350 --> 00:01:24,410
have changed a lot.

15
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:26,950
How so?

16
00:01:30,570 --> 00:01:31,300
Your stamina

17
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,250
is much better.

18
00:01:40,050 --> 00:01:41,110
What are you doing?

19
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:42,900
Looks like you've earned a lot of money.

20
00:02:44,420 --> 00:02:45,480
Why do you say that?

21
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:50,970
'Cause it doesn't seem like you.

22
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:53,970
True.

23
00:02:55,730 --> 00:02:58,329
I really want to leave here
as soon as possible.

24
00:03:01,730 --> 00:03:02,930
Have you thought of me

25
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:05,320
in the past 5 years?

26
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,100
Why are you asking me that?

27
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:15,580
Tell me.

28
00:03:19,740 --> 00:03:22,100
Every day, all day—

29
00:03:23,480 --> 00:03:25,280
you were all I could think about.

30
00:03:38,050 --> 00:03:41,090
You don't mind if I take off
this police uniform, do you?

31
00:03:41,090 --> 00:03:41,550
Mm.

32
00:03:42,270 --> 00:03:43,270
Take it off for me.

33
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,610
You've lost a lot of weight.

34
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,020
Yoo Sehyun.

35
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:04,050
Give me a sec.

36
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:14,280
Yeah, shoot.

37
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:17,279
Now?

38
00:04:20,329 --> 00:04:20,920
Got it.

39
00:04:21,470 --> 00:04:22,600
I'll be right there.

40
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:36,909
You're hiding something from me, right?

41
00:04:37,620 --> 00:04:39,220
It has nothing to do with you.

42
00:04:40,950 --> 00:04:41,550
Sung Ho.

43
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,980
You are a cop,

44
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,140
and I am a nightclub owner.

45
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:47,980
From the very beginning,

46
00:04:47,980 --> 00:04:49,840
we were never from the same world.

47
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,180
And that kiss just now?

48
00:04:57,880 --> 00:04:59,540
It meant absolutely nothing.

49
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,120
Five years

50
00:05:02,420 --> 00:05:04,680
is enough time to change a person's fate.

51
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,300
I won't be like before,

52
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,370
having only you in my eyes.

53
00:05:10,730 --> 00:05:13,190
Because I'm no longer
the person I used to be.

54
00:05:24,340 --> 00:05:24,930
Sung Ho.

55
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:29,780
Do you know what's
the most invaluable thing in the world?

56
00:05:30,350 --> 00:05:31,380
It's feelings.

57
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:34,640
You wear that police uniform,

58
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,370
standing in a glamorous world.

59
00:05:37,790 --> 00:05:40,900
Full of justice, perfect, and clean.

60
00:05:44,980 --> 00:05:45,570
While I am just

61
00:05:45,570 --> 00:05:47,050
a nightclub owner.

62
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:52,320
A person struggling
to survive in the shadows.

63
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:56,580
From the very beginning,
we were never from the same world.

64
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,840
Don't come here anymore.

65
00:05:59,060 --> 00:06:00,060
You get in the way.

66
00:06:02,650 --> 00:06:03,250
Oh, right.

67
00:06:04,090 --> 00:06:05,750
It was the same in high school.

68
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:09,230
Your parents were the school's sponsors.

69
00:06:09,920 --> 00:06:10,650
And I was just

70
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:16,010
a student who couldn't go to school
without a scholarship.

71
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:23,680
Yoo Sehyun!

72
00:06:30,130 --> 00:06:32,130
Say whatever you want, I don't care.

73
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,320
But if you break the law,

74
00:06:37,150 --> 00:06:38,810
I will definitely arrest you.

75
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:07,440
Kwon Hyukjae.

76
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:10,740
What exactly do you want to do?

77
00:07:16,130 --> 00:07:16,850
Sung Ho.

78
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,250
I'm sorry.

79
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:41,580
Mayor Li.

80
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:45,010
You must become the president.

81
00:07:46,970 --> 00:07:47,820
Because I have

82
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:51,020
bet everything I have on you.

83
00:08:08,880 --> 00:08:10,680
Minho, it's time to get off work.

84
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:13,240
You can take off your police uniform.

85
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,200
Yes.

86
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,550
How about we play a game?

87
00:08:59,230 --> 00:08:59,750
Hmm?

88
00:09:42,820 --> 00:09:43,240
Hit me.

89
00:10:02,180 --> 00:10:02,640
Harder.

90
00:10:15,450 --> 00:10:17,250
I'm telling you to hit me harder.

91
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:25,160
Harder. More.

92
00:10:37,290 --> 00:10:37,820
More!

93
00:10:41,020 --> 00:10:41,880
Use some force.

94
00:10:54,580 --> 00:10:55,460
Damn it.

95
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,110
Damn it.

96
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:09,750
Can I come in?

97
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:11,170
Come in.

98
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:17,670
Are there

99
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,050
any special instructions?

100
00:11:25,310 --> 00:11:27,180
There are many things suspicious
about those nightclubs in Gangnam,

101
00:11:27,180 --> 00:11:28,910
but there is no solid evidence.

102
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:31,980
Keep an eye on them.

103
00:11:32,380 --> 00:11:34,240
Report to me if there's anything.

104
00:11:34,520 --> 00:11:35,520
Yes, understood.

105
00:11:36,180 --> 00:11:37,140
Also, Sung Ho...

106
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,020
You and Yoo Sehyun
from the Gangnam nightclub,

107
00:11:42,020 --> 00:11:44,080
were high school classmates, right?

108
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,880
Yes, we were classmates.

109
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:50,950
But we haven't contacted each other
since then.

110
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:52,810
We just ran into each other today.

111
00:11:54,710 --> 00:11:55,840
Ran into each other?

112
00:11:59,620 --> 00:12:00,410
But I heard

113
00:12:01,180 --> 00:12:03,180
you two used to be very close.

114
00:12:04,280 --> 00:12:05,980
You even dated.

115
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:11,680
That was all in high school.

116
00:12:13,190 --> 00:12:14,750
It was just playing around.

117
00:12:16,920 --> 00:12:19,180
We have nothing to do with each other now.

118
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:24,750
Sung Ho.

119
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:28,980
You just came back.

120
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:32,250
You must separate
public and private matters.

121
00:12:32,250 --> 00:12:32,980
Understand?

122
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:36,390
Officer Kwon,

123
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:40,950
are you familiar with Yoo Sehyun?

124
00:12:43,460 --> 00:12:45,990
We met before
when I was investigating a case.

125
00:12:47,420 --> 00:12:48,680
Don't take it to heart.

126
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:51,550
Go back and rest.

127
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:28,720
Minho,

128
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:33,510
Yoo Sehyun is the informant
I planted next to Sung Ho.

129
00:13:35,380 --> 00:13:37,050
Keep a close eye on him.

130
00:13:37,220 --> 00:13:37,780
Got it?

131
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:40,250
Yes.

132
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:42,750
Go.

133
00:13:58,580 --> 00:14:00,120
Bastard.

134
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:25,800
Were you happy to see Sung Ho yesterday?

135
00:14:30,040 --> 00:14:31,980
How far do you want me to go?

136
00:14:35,130 --> 00:14:36,790
You told me to see him, so I did.

137
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:40,760
You told me to distance myself, so I did.

138
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:44,720
But how far do you intend

139
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:48,270
on bossing me around like this?

140
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:27,610
Damn it.

141
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:38,740
Sehyun,

142
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,750
you are now the boss of Gangnam Palace.

143
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:44,950
Okay?

144
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:47,550
And Sung Ho is

145
00:15:47,610 --> 00:15:49,350
a line you must never cross.

146
00:15:51,850 --> 00:15:54,020
If you dare to cross it,
you both will die.

147
00:15:54,020 --> 00:15:54,450
Got it?

148
00:15:58,050 --> 00:15:59,220
It's been 5 years.

149
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:02,350
It's already the 5th year.

150
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:06,350
You promised me.

151
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:07,950
Huh?

152
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:11,150
That as long as I hold on for 5 years,

153
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:14,590
you promised I could return
to the police force.

154
00:16:14,920 --> 00:16:15,450
You also promised me

155
00:16:15,450 --> 00:16:17,250
I could return to Sung Ho's side.

156
00:16:20,760 --> 00:16:22,290
That promise still counts.

157
00:16:23,900 --> 00:16:25,100
But Sung Ho came back—

158
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:27,000
that is the variable.

159
00:16:28,680 --> 00:16:31,080
What if you let your feelings
get in the way?

160
00:16:31,260 --> 00:16:31,590
Hmm?

161
00:16:39,220 --> 00:16:40,750
Please don't touch Sung Ho.

162
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:43,980
If you promise me that,

163
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,740
I will keep doing this.

164
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:56,310
What are you talking about?

165
00:16:58,580 --> 00:16:59,050
Hey.

166
00:17:01,940 --> 00:17:02,290
I

167
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:06,380
had no intention of touching him.

168
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,609
Besides, there's no value in doing so.

169
00:17:11,650 --> 00:17:13,510
Don't let those pointless feelings

170
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:14,579
ruin everything.

171
00:17:16,050 --> 00:17:16,780
Understand?

172
00:17:24,819 --> 00:17:25,880
Oh, one more thing.

173
00:17:27,150 --> 00:17:28,610
You know Kim Minho, right?

174
00:17:30,060 --> 00:17:32,390
He is my informant
I placed next to Sung Ho.

175
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:36,410
You should also watch your words
and actions.

176
00:18:48,120 --> 00:18:48,750
Hello?

177
00:18:48,890 --> 00:18:49,520
Sung Ho.

178
00:18:50,220 --> 00:18:51,680
Can't recognize my voice?

179
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:52,890
I'm Yoo Sehyun.

180
00:18:52,950 --> 00:18:53,820
Yoo Sehyun?

181
00:18:56,820 --> 00:18:58,070
How did you get my phone number?

182
00:18:58,070 --> 00:18:59,250
Let's meet at Gangnam Palace.

183
00:18:59,250 --> 00:19:00,270
Let's talk properly when you get here.

184
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,200
What do you want?

185
00:19:02,610 --> 00:19:03,170
Sung Ho,

186
00:19:03,690 --> 00:19:04,210
aren't you curious

187
00:19:04,210 --> 00:19:06,410
why I suddenly disappeared 5 years ago?

188
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:09,180
Stop trying to test the boundaries.

189
00:19:10,530 --> 00:19:12,390
You are a club owner, and I am a cop.

190
00:19:12,420 --> 00:19:13,870
I have nothing to say to you.

191
00:19:13,870 --> 00:19:14,750
Nothing to say?

192
00:19:14,890 --> 00:19:15,950
Why I gave up my dream of becoming a cop

193
00:19:15,950 --> 00:19:17,210
and chose to run a club—

194
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:17,990
come if you want to know the reason.

195
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:18,950
I'll tell you everything.

196
00:19:18,950 --> 00:19:19,380
Fine,

197
00:19:20,420 --> 00:19:20,980
I'll go.

198
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:23,420
8 PM. I'll wait for you.

199
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:25,230
But if you dare to mess with me,

200
00:19:27,620 --> 00:19:29,350
I won't let you get away with it.

201
00:19:35,830 --> 00:19:37,430
The truth from 5 years ago...

202
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:06,570
[Sin and Love]

